1 Changes in county-level employment after covid (2020 Q2)

statedata <- read_fst("/home/dimuthu/SSRN Oct 2021/Economic Shock/state_quarter_economic_data.fst",as.data.table = T)
names(statedata)[3:25] <- paste0("state_",names(statedata)[3:25])
statedata <- statedata[data_month %in% c(as.Date("2020-04-01"))]
statedata[,data_month:=list(NULL)]

countydata <- read_fst("/home/dimuthu/SSRN Oct 2021/Economic Shock/county_quarter_economic_data.fst",as.data.table = T)
names(countydata)[3:11] <- paste0("county_",names(countydata)[3:11])
countydata <- countydata[data_month %in% c(as.Date("2020-04-01"))]
countydata[,data_month:=list(NULL)]

g1 <- ggplot(countydata,aes(x=county_emp))+geom_density(fill="dodgerblue2")+labs(x="Employment",y="")+theme_minimal()
g2 <- ggplot(countydata,aes(x=county_emp_incbelowmed))+geom_density(fill="dodgerblue2")+labs(x="Employment < median income",y="")+theme_minimal()
g3 <- ggplot(countydata,aes(x=county_emp_incabovemed))+geom_density(fill="dodgerblue2")+labs(x="Employment > median income",y="")+theme_minimal()
g4 <- ggplot(countydata[abs(county_revenue_all)<1],aes(x=county_revenue_all))+geom_density(fill="dodgerblue2")+labs(x="SMB Reveue ",y="")+theme_minimal()
grid.arrange(g1,g2,g3,g4)

2 Default Regression

controls <- "+default_probability+I(fico_score/100)+log(1+annual_income)+dti+borrower_age+I(borrower_age^2)+log(1+number_of_accounts)+log(1+inquiries_past_6_months)+log(1+total_balance)+log(1+credit_history)+log(1+num_accounts_opened_in_past_12_months)+log(1+revolving_pct*100)+log(1+mortgage_pct*100)+log(1+creditcard_utilization*100)+log(1+g051s_percentage_of_trades_ever_delinquent*100)+log(loan_amount)|state_year+contract_years|0|state"

covlabs <- c("Employment","Employment(< median income)","Employment(> median income)","Revenue","Default probability","Credit score/100","log(Annual income)","Debt-to-income","Age of the borrower","Age of the borrower2","log(Number of accounts)","log(Number of inquiries)","log(Total liabilities)","log(Credit history)","log(No of recently opened accounts)","log(Pct. of revolving liabilities)","log(Pct. of mortgage liabilities)","log(Credit card utilization)","log(Pct. trades ever delinquent)","log(Loan amount)")

r <- list()
r[[1]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("delinquent_q3~county_emp",controls)),data=loan_sample[annual_income>0])
r[[2]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("delinquent_q3~county_emp",controls)),data=loan_sample[annual_income>0 & standardized_job_type %in% c("Food or Hotel Services")])
r[[3]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("delinquent_q3~county_emp_incbelowmed",controls)),data=loan_sample[annual_income>0 & annual_income<40000])
r[[4]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("delinquent_q3~county_emp_incabovemed",controls)),data=loan_sample[annual_income>0 & annual_income>=40000])
r[[5]] <- felm(as.formula(paste0("delinquent_q3~county_revenue_all",controls)),data=loan_sample[annual_income>0])


stargazer(r,type="text",no.space = T,omit.stat=c("ser", "rsq"),style = "qje",omit.table.layout = "n",
          covariate.labels = c(covlabs),
          dep.var.labels.include = F,
          add.lines=list(c("State*Year",rep("Y",6)),c("Term",rep("Y",6)),c("Sample","Full","Food or Hotel","Income<40k","Income>40k","Full")))

loans <- read_fst(path="/home/dimuthu/SSRN Oct 2021/Predictability/loans.fst",as.data.table = T)
loans[,maturity_date:=accepted_date+contract_years*365]
loans <- loans[maturity_date>="2021-10-30"] #& loan_contract_id %in% perdata$loan_contract_id
loans[,industry:=ifelse(standardized_job_type %in% c("Food or Hotel Services"),"Food and Hotel","0ther")]
loan_contract_ids <- paste(loans$loan_contract_id,collapse = ",")

past_due_data <- runQuery(paste0("select 
                            dls.as_of_date,
                            dls.loan_contract_id,
                            dls.days_past_due,
                            dls.loan_modified
                           from monolith.daily_loan_snapshots as dls
                           where dls.loan_contract_id in (",loan_contract_ids,")
                           and dls.days_past_due>5 or dls.loan_modified=True
                           "))
past_due_data[,loan_modified:=ifelse(loan_modified==T,1,0)]     
past_due_data[,as_of_date:=as.Date(paste0(year(as_of_date),"-",month(as_of_date),"-01"))]

past_due_data <- past_due_data[,.(days_past_due=max(days_past_due,na.rm=T),loan_modified=max(loan_modified,na.rm=T)),by=.(loan_contract_id,as_of_date)]
loan_month <- fread(file="/home/dimuthu/SSRN Oct 2021/Covid shock/loan_month.csv")
names(loan_month) <- c("dls_month","upstart_id")
loan_month[,dls_month:=as.Date(dls_month)]

loan_month <- merge(loan_month,loans[,c("upstart_id","loan_contract_id","college","hourly","fico_score","computer","debtconsolidation")],by="upstart_id")
loan_month <- merge(loan_month,past_due_data,by.x=c("loan_contract_id","dls_month"),by.y=c("loan_contract_id","as_of_date"),all.x=T)

loan_month[,loan_modified:=ifelse(is.na(loan_modified),0,loan_modified)]
loan_month[,days_past_due:=ifelse(is.na(days_past_due),0,days_past_due)]

loan_month[,low_credit_score_640:=ifelse(fico_score<640,1,0)]
